{
  "episode_id": "PD-2026-015-theranos",
  "method": "master-vo-timeline faster-whisper word timestamps aligned to locked script",
  "timeline_seconds": 705.259,
  "cues": [
    {
      "id": "CAP-0001",
      "start": 11.56,
      "end": 13.1,
      "text": "A single drop of blood.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0002",
      "start": 13.76,
      "end": 16.22,
      "text": "A company worth nine billion dollars.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0003",
      "start": 16.22,
      "end": 18.56,
      "text": "A young founder on the cover of every",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0004",
      "start": 18.56,
      "end": 21.12,
      "text": "magazine, hailed as the next Steve Jobs.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0005",
      "start": 21.12,
      "end": 22.44,
      "text": "And underneath all of it,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0006",
      "start": 22.44,
      "end": 25.06,
      "text": "a machine that did not actually do what",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0007",
      "start": 25.06,
      "end": 27.8,
      "text": "the world was told it could do.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0008",
      "start": 28.94,
      "end": 32.28,
      "text": "The story of Theranos is the most famous",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0009",
      "start": 32.28,
      "end": 34.34,
      "text": "fraud of the startup era — and it",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0010",
      "start": 34.34,
      "end": 37.66,
      "text": "ends with a question that hangs over every",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0011",
      "start": 37.66,
      "end": 39.0,
      "text": "bold promise ever made to investors:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0012",
      "start": 39.0,
      "end": 39.725,
      "text": "when does selling a dream become a crime?",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0001"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0013",
      "start": 47.34,
      "end": 49.9,
      "text": "For this whole series, we have watched the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0014",
      "start": 49.9,
      "end": 51.98,
      "text": "power of the state pressing against one person",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0015",
      "start": 53.65,
      "end": 54.54,
      "text": "— searching you, tracking you,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0016",
      "start": 54.9,
      "end": 56.92,
      "text": "taking from you, following you home.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0017",
      "start": 57.56,
      "end": 59.5,
      "text": "This final story turns the camera completely",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0018",
      "start": 59.5,
      "end": 59.92,
      "text": "around.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0019",
      "start": 60.56,
      "end": 62.7,
      "text": "Here, it is one person whose words reach",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0020",
      "start": 62.7,
      "end": 63.3,
      "text": "everyone:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0021",
      "start": 63.9,
      "end": 65.88,
      "text": "the investors who put in hundreds of millions,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0022",
      "start": 65.88,
      "end": 68.24,
      "text": "and the patients who trusted their blood to",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0023",
      "start": 68.24,
      "end": 68.74,
      "text": "a machine.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0024",
      "start": 69.56,
      "end": 71.0,
      "text": "Over the next twelve minutes:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0025",
      "start": 71.36,
      "end": 73.64,
      "text": "how Theranos rose, how it fell,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0026",
      "start": 74.08,
      "end": 76.32,
      "text": "and what a jury decided actually crossed the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0027",
      "start": 76.32,
      "end": 79.72,
      "text": "line from ambition into fraud — because that",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0028",
      "start": 79.72,
      "end": 82.52,
      "text": "line, it turns out, is narrower and stranger",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0029",
      "start": 82.52,
      "end": 83.6,
      "text": "than you might think.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0002"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0030",
      "start": 95.33,
      "end": 98.42,
      "text": "It begins in 2003, with a nineteen-year-old who",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0003"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0031",
      "start": 98.42,
      "end": 100.3,
      "text": "drops out of Stanford to start a company.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0003"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0032",
      "start": 100.98,
      "end": 102.2,
      "text": "Her name is Elizabeth Holmes,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0003"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0033",
      "start": 102.6,
      "end": 104.4,
      "text": "and her idea is genuinely seductive.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0003"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0034",
      "start": 104.4,
      "end": 106.66,
      "text": "Today, a blood test means a needle,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0035",
      "start": 107.22,
      "end": 109.24,
      "text": "a vial, a lab, a wait.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0036",
      "start": 110.14,
      "end": 111.86,
      "text": "Holmes promised to erase all of that.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0037",
      "start": 112.4,
      "end": 115.48,
      "text": "Her company, Theranos, said its device — called",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0038",
      "start": 115.48,
      "end": 117.94,
      "text": "the Edison — could run hundreds of tests",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0039",
      "start": 117.94,
      "end": 120.62,
      "text": "from a single, painless drop of blood from",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0040",
      "start": 120.62,
      "end": 122.66,
      "text": "your finger, quickly and cheaply,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0041",
      "start": 122.96,
      "end": 125.2,
      "text": "maybe one day in every drugstore and home.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0042",
      "start": 125.76,
      "end": 127.76,
      "text": "If it were real, it would change medicine.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0043",
      "start": 128.48,
      "end": 129.96,
      "text": "That \"if\" is the whole story.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0004"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0044",
      "start": 130.32,
      "end": 132.12,
      "text": "And the world wanted it to be real.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0045",
      "start": 132.92,
      "end": 133.86,
      "text": "Money poured in.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0046",
      "start": 134.68,
      "end": 136.56,
      "text": "At its peak, around 2014,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0047",
      "start": 136.88,
      "end": 139.0,
      "text": "Theranos was valued at roughly nine billion",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0048",
      "start": 139.82,
      "end": 142.58,
      "text": "dollars, briefly making Holmes a paper billionaire",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0049",
      "start": 142.58,
      "end": 144.62,
      "text": "and one of the most celebrated founders in",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0050",
      "start": 145.32,
      "end": 145.56,
      "text": "America.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0051",
      "start": 145.56,
      "end": 148.58,
      "text": "Its board filled with famous names — former",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0052",
      "start": 148.58,
      "end": 150.38,
      "text": "statesmen and military leaders.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0053",
      "start": 150.38,
      "end": 152.76,
      "text": "It struck a deal with the pharmacy chain",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0054",
      "start": 152.76,
      "end": 154.799,
      "text": "Walgreens to put its testing in some stores.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0005"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0055",
      "start": 162.4,
      "end": 164.56,
      "text": "And the prestige fed on itself.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0056",
      "start": 165.32,
      "end": 167.24,
      "text": "A board of household names made the company",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0057",
      "start": 167.24,
      "end": 170.66,
      "text": "look unimpeachable; a soaring valuation made",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0058",
      "start": 170.66,
      "end": 172.46,
      "text": "skeptics look foolish for doubting.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0059",
      "start": 173.08,
      "end": 175.46,
      "text": "Each famous believer became a reason for the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0060",
      "start": 175.46,
      "end": 177.24,
      "text": "next person not to look too closely.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0061",
      "start": 177.9,
      "end": 179.06,
      "text": "That is how a story,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0062",
      "start": 179.06,
      "end": 181.2,
      "text": "more than a product, can carry a company",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0063",
      "start": 181.2,
      "end": 181.72,
      "text": "for years.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0006"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0064",
      "start": 182.38,
      "end": 183.88,
      "text": "Notice what made this so powerful.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0065",
      "start": 184.56,
      "end": 186.58,
      "text": "It was not just a product; it was",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0066",
      "start": 186.58,
      "end": 189.1,
      "text": "a story — a brilliant young woman,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0067",
      "start": 189.62,
      "end": 192.8,
      "text": "a revolutionary machine, a future where a drop",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0068",
      "start": 192.8,
      "end": 194.34,
      "text": "of blood could save your life.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0069",
      "start": 195.46,
      "end": 197.8,
      "text": "Investors, reporters, and partners all wanted to",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0070",
      "start": 197.8,
      "end": 198.48,
      "text": "be part of it.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0071",
      "start": 199.02,
      "end": 201.12,
      "text": "And a beautiful enough story can make very",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0072",
      "start": 201.12,
      "end": 203.62,
      "text": "smart people stop asking the most basic question:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0073",
      "start": 204.52,
      "end": 206.0,
      "text": "does the thing actually work?",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0007"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0074",
      "start": 217.62,
      "end": 220.48,
      "text": "In 2015, someone finally asked it in print.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0008"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0075",
      "start": 221.2,
      "end": 222.32,
      "text": "A Wall Street Journal reporter,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0008"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0076",
      "start": 222.58,
      "end": 225.08,
      "text": "John Carreyrou, published an investigation built",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0008"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0077",
      "start": 225.08,
      "end": 227.06,
      "text": "on internal documents and whistleblowers.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0008"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0078",
      "start": 227.74,
      "end": 229.18,
      "text": "What it reported was devastating.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0079",
      "start": 229.86,
      "end": 231.92,
      "text": "The Edison did not work as advertised.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0080",
      "start": 232.7,
      "end": 234.72,
      "text": "Behind the scenes, the investigation said,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0081",
      "start": 235.48,
      "end": 237.28,
      "text": "Theranos was running many of its blood tests",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0082",
      "start": 237.48,
      "end": 239.04,
      "text": "not on its own revolutionary device,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0083",
      "start": 239.72,
      "end": 242.2,
      "text": "but on ordinary commercial machines made by other",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0084",
      "start": 242.2,
      "end": 244.68,
      "text": "companies — the very kind of equipment it",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0085",
      "start": 244.68,
      "end": 245.7,
      "text": "claimed to have replaced.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0086",
      "start": 246.14,
      "end": 248.8,
      "text": "And the finger-prick results it did produce had",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0087",
      "start": 248.8,
      "end": 250.3,
      "text": "serious accuracy problems.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0009"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0088",
      "start": 250.86,
      "end": 252.94,
      "text": "For a tech demo, unreliable results are an",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0010"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0089",
      "start": 252.94,
      "end": 253.34,
      "text": "embarrassment.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0010"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0090",
      "start": 254.08,
      "end": 256.16,
      "text": "For a medical test, they are something else",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0010"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0091",
      "start": 256.16,
      "end": 258.92,
      "text": "entirely — because real people were making real",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0010"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0092",
      "start": 258.92,
      "end": 260.68,
      "text": "health decisions based on the numbers.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0010"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0093",
      "start": 261.2,
      "end": 262.52,
      "text": "From there, the fall was fast.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0094",
      "start": 263.24,
      "end": 264.1,
      "text": "Regulators moved in.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0095",
      "start": 264.66,
      "end": 266.12,
      "text": "The Walgreens partnership ended.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0096",
      "start": 266.66,
      "end": 269.48,
      "text": "In 2018, the Securities and Exchange Commission",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0097",
      "start": 269.48,
      "end": 272.54,
      "text": "charged Holmes with fraud, and she settled those",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0098",
      "start": 272.54,
      "end": 275.26,
      "text": "civil charges without admitting or denying",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0099",
      "start": 275.26,
      "end": 278.3,
      "text": "wrongdoing — paying a penalty and accepting a",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0100",
      "start": 278.3,
      "end": 279.8,
      "text": "ban from leading a public company.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0101",
      "start": 280.44,
      "end": 282.42,
      "text": "That same year, Theranos dissolved.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0102",
      "start": 282.92,
      "end": 285.28,
      "text": "The nine-billion-dollar company was worth nothing.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0011"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0103",
      "start": 292.16,
      "end": 294.68,
      "text": "But a collapsed company and a civil settlement",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0104",
      "start": 294.68,
      "end": 296.16,
      "text": "are not the same as a crime.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0105",
      "start": 296.76,
      "end": 300.279,
      "text": "The harder question — the criminal one —",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0106",
      "start": 300.28,
      "end": 300.34,
      "text": "was still coming.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0107",
      "start": 300.86,
      "end": 303.94,
      "text": "Did Elizabeth Holmes simply fail at something hard",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0108",
      "start": 303.94,
      "end": 305.06,
      "text": "while believing in it?",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0109",
      "start": 305.38,
      "end": 307.8,
      "text": "Or did she knowingly deceive the people who",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0110",
      "start": 307.8,
      "end": 308.42,
      "text": "trusted her?",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0111",
      "start": 309.12,
      "end": 310.54,
      "text": "Those are not the same thing,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0112",
      "start": 310.86,
      "end": 312.8,
      "text": "and the difference between them is the difference",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0113",
      "start": 312.8,
      "end": 314.98,
      "text": "between a sad story and a prison sentence.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0012"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0114",
      "start": 326.48,
      "end": 328.58,
      "text": "That question went to a federal court,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0115",
      "start": 328.58,
      "end": 330.46,
      "text": "in the case United States v.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0116",
      "start": 330.46,
      "end": 330.86,
      "text": "Holmes.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0117",
      "start": 331.84,
      "end": 333.04,
      "text": "And to understand the verdict,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0118",
      "start": 333.4,
      "end": 335.84,
      "text": "you have to understand what fraud actually is,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0119",
      "start": 335.84,
      "end": 336.3,
      "text": "legally.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0013"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0120",
      "start": 337.3,
      "end": 338.26,
      "text": "Fraud is not failure.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0121",
      "start": 338.96,
      "end": 340.8,
      "text": "It is not even lying in some loose,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0122",
      "start": 340.8,
      "end": 341.6,
      "text": "everyday sense.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0123",
      "start": 342.6,
      "end": 345.86,
      "text": "Criminal fraud requires intent to deceive — proof",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0124",
      "start": 345.86,
      "end": 348.5,
      "text": "that a person knowingly made false statements to",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0125",
      "start": 348.5,
      "end": 350.9,
      "text": "get something of value from someone who relied",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0126",
      "start": 350.9,
      "end": 351.34,
      "text": "on them.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0127",
      "start": 351.84,
      "end": 354.26,
      "text": "A founder who genuinely believes in a product",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0128",
      "start": 354.26,
      "end": 356.38,
      "text": "that does not pan out has not committed",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0129",
      "start": 356.38,
      "end": 356.86,
      "text": "a crime.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0130",
      "start": 357.45,
      "end": 359.72,
      "text": "A founder who knows the truth and hides",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0131",
      "start": 359.72,
      "end": 361.38,
      "text": "it to keep the money flowing has.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0132",
      "start": 362.18,
      "end": 364.12,
      "text": "The entire trial was a fight over which",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0133",
      "start": 364.12,
      "end": 365.92,
      "text": "of those describes Elizabeth Holmes.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0014"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0134",
      "start": 366.48,
      "end": 368.56,
      "text": "At trial, the two sides told that exact",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0135",
      "start": 368.56,
      "end": 369.52,
      "text": "split-screen story.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0136",
      "start": 370.7,
      "end": 372.6,
      "text": "Prosecutors argued that Holmes knew about the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0137",
      "start": 372.6,
      "end": 374.26,
      "text": "device's failures and hid them,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0138",
      "start": 374.66,
      "end": 376.84,
      "text": "pointing to internal results and warnings she had",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0139",
      "start": 376.84,
      "end": 377.16,
      "text": "received.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0140",
      "start": 377.82,
      "end": 379.72,
      "text": "Her defense argued that she was a true",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0141",
      "start": 379.72,
      "end": 382.12,
      "text": "believer who genuinely thought the technology",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0142",
      "start": 382.12,
      "end": 384.56,
      "text": "would work, and that being wrong is not",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0143",
      "start": 384.56,
      "end": 385.28,
      "text": "the same as lying.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0144",
      "start": 385.28,
      "end": 387.6,
      "text": "The jury's job was to decide,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0145",
      "start": 387.88,
      "end": 390.66,
      "text": "count by count, which story the evidence supported",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0146",
      "start": 390.66,
      "end": 392.06,
      "text": "beyond a reasonable doubt.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0015"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0147",
      "start": 392.6,
      "end": 395.16,
      "text": "On January 3rd, 2022, the jury delivered a",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0148",
      "start": 395.16,
      "end": 397.02,
      "text": "verdict — and it was not a simple",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0149",
      "start": 397.02,
      "end": 397.3,
      "text": "one.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0150",
      "start": 397.9,
      "end": 400.04,
      "text": "It convicted Holmes on four counts of fraud",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0151",
      "start": 400.04,
      "end": 400.86,
      "text": "against investors:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0152",
      "start": 401.46,
      "end": 404.28,
      "text": "one count of conspiracy, and three counts of",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0153",
      "start": 404.28,
      "end": 407.72,
      "text": "wire fraud, for deceiving specific investors who",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0154",
      "start": 407.72,
      "end": 408.74,
      "text": "had put in large sums.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0155",
      "start": 409.48,
      "end": 411.3,
      "text": "On those counts, the jury found that she",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0156",
      "start": 411.3,
      "end": 413.58,
      "text": "had crossed the line — that she knowingly",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0157",
      "start": 413.58,
      "end": 415.42,
      "text": "deceived the people funding the company.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0016"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0158",
      "start": 435.34,
      "end": 437.42,
      "text": "But on the counts that accused her of",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0159",
      "start": 437.42,
      "end": 440.16,
      "text": "defrauding patients, the jury found her not",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0160",
      "start": 440.16,
      "end": 440.62,
      "text": "guilty.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0161",
      "start": 441.06,
      "end": 442.84,
      "text": "And on three more investor counts,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0162",
      "start": 443.12,
      "end": 444.6,
      "text": "the jurors could not agree at all,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0163",
      "start": 445.16,
      "end": 447.18,
      "text": "so the judge declared a mistrial on those.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0164",
      "start": 447.94,
      "end": 450.24,
      "text": "Convicted on some, acquitted on others,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0165",
      "start": 450.86,
      "end": 451.76,
      "text": "deadlocked on the rest.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0017"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0166",
      "start": 452.36,
      "end": 454.22,
      "text": "It is tempting to read the patient acquittals",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0167",
      "start": 454.22,
      "end": 456.74,
      "text": "as a verdict that the technology was fine,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0168",
      "start": 456.74,
      "end": 458.38,
      "text": "or that no one was hurt.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0169",
      "start": 459.16,
      "end": 459.9,
      "text": "It is not.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0170",
      "start": 460.78,
      "end": 463.26,
      "text": "An acquittal means only that the prosecution did",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0171",
      "start": 463.26,
      "end": 465.92,
      "text": "not prove those particular charges beyond a",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0172",
      "start": 465.92,
      "end": 468.52,
      "text": "reasonable doubt — the highest bar in law",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0173",
      "start": 470.624,
      "end": 471.82,
      "text": "— not that the underlying conduct was harmless.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0174",
      "start": 472.68,
      "end": 475.02,
      "text": "One juror later suggested the patient link was",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0175",
      "start": 475.02,
      "end": 477.58,
      "text": "simply harder to pin directly on Holmes.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0176",
      "start": 478.26,
      "end": 480.18,
      "text": "And the contrast makes the point sharply:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0177",
      "start": 481.12,
      "end": 484.58,
      "text": "Theranos's former president, Ramesh Balwani — her",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0178",
      "start": 484.58,
      "end": 487.4,
      "text": "business and former romantic partner — was tried",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0179",
      "start": 487.4,
      "end": 489.62,
      "text": "separately, and he was convicted on all twelve",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0180",
      "start": 489.62,
      "end": 491.88,
      "text": "counts, including the patient counts,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0181",
      "start": 492.24,
      "end": 494.16,
      "text": "and sentenced to nearly thirteen years.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0018"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0182",
      "start": 494.68,
      "end": 495.44,
      "text": "As for Holmes:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0183",
      "start": 495.66,
      "end": 498.14,
      "text": "in November 2022, she was sentenced to about",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0184",
      "start": 498.14,
      "end": 500.02,
      "text": "eleven years and three months in federal prison.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0185",
      "start": 500.84,
      "end": 502.74,
      "text": "The young woman once compared to Steve Jobs",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0186",
      "start": 502.74,
      "end": 505.18,
      "text": "was now a convicted fraudster — but,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0187",
      "start": 505.18,
      "end": 507.68,
      "text": "precisely, a fraudster of investors,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0188",
      "start": 507.68,
      "end": 510.6,
      "text": "on four specific counts proven to a jury.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0019"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0189",
      "start": 522.16,
      "end": 524.34,
      "text": "So where, exactly, is the line that Holmes",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0190",
      "start": 524.34,
      "end": 524.66,
      "text": "crossed?",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0191",
      "start": 525.36,
      "end": 527.22,
      "text": "Because here is the uncomfortable truth:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0192",
      "start": 527.82,
      "end": 529.74,
      "text": "a lot of what Theranos did looks like",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0193",
      "start": 529.74,
      "end": 531.02,
      "text": "ordinary startup behavior.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0194",
      "start": 532.3,
      "end": 534.3,
      "text": "Founders pitch a future that does not exist",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0195",
      "start": 534.3,
      "end": 534.62,
      "text": "yet.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0196",
      "start": 535.28,
      "end": 537.66,
      "text": "They project confidence they do not fully feel.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0197",
      "start": 538.54,
      "end": 540.04,
      "text": "\"Fake it till you make it\" is practically",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0198",
      "start": 540.04,
      "end": 542.62,
      "text": "a Silicon Valley slogan, and most of the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0199",
      "start": 542.62,
      "end": 543.8,
      "text": "time the law leaves it alone.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0020"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0200",
      "start": 544.38,
      "end": 545.8,
      "text": "The line is intent and reliance.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0201",
      "start": 546.84,
      "end": 548.38,
      "text": "Selling an ambitious vision is legal.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0202",
      "start": 549.16,
      "end": 551.86,
      "text": "Knowingly telling people something false — that a",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0203",
      "start": 551.86,
      "end": 553.52,
      "text": "machine works when you know it does not",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0204",
      "start": 554.0,
      "end": 555.7,
      "text": "— to get them to hand over money",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0205",
      "start": 555.7,
      "end": 557.04,
      "text": "they would not otherwise risk,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0206",
      "start": 557.04,
      "end": 557.86,
      "text": "is fraud.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0207",
      "start": 558.82,
      "end": 560.76,
      "text": "The jury concluded that, with investors,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0208",
      "start": 560.76,
      "end": 563.12,
      "text": "Holmes had done exactly that.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0021"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0209",
      "start": 570.3,
      "end": 572.42,
      "text": "And there is a reason the stakes felt",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0210",
      "start": 572.42,
      "end": 575.14,
      "text": "higher here than in an ordinary bad investment.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0211",
      "start": 575.86,
      "end": 577.32,
      "text": "A failed app costs you money.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0212",
      "start": 577.88,
      "end": 579.76,
      "text": "A blood test that gives the wrong answer",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0213",
      "start": 579.76,
      "end": 581.28,
      "text": "can cost you a diagnosis.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0214",
      "start": 582.04,
      "end": 584.28,
      "text": "That is why the patient dimension haunted the",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0215",
      "start": 584.28,
      "end": 587.14,
      "text": "whole case, even where the specific counts did",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0216",
      "start": 587.14,
      "end": 589.92,
      "text": "not stick to Holmes — and why Balwani's",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0217",
      "start": 589.92,
      "end": 592.02,
      "text": "conviction on those counts matters to the full",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0218",
      "start": 592.02,
      "end": 592.4,
      "text": "picture.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0022"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0219",
      "start": 604.16,
      "end": 605.84,
      "text": "Theranos is where this series ends,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0220",
      "start": 605.84,
      "end": 607.92,
      "text": "and it is a fitting place — because",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0221",
      "start": 607.92,
      "end": 609.82,
      "text": "under every episode we have watched,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0222",
      "start": 609.82,
      "end": 611.14,
      "text": "there has been one question,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0223",
      "start": 611.14,
      "end": 612.64,
      "text": "wearing different costumes.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0224",
      "start": 613.1,
      "end": 614.62,
      "text": "The police searching your pockets,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0225",
      "start": 615.04,
      "end": 617.46,
      "text": "tracking your phone, taking your property,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0226",
      "start": 617.98,
      "end": 620.5,
      "text": "swabbing your cheek, following you to your door",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0227",
      "start": 621.223,
      "end": 623.22,
      "text": "— and now a founder selling a miracle",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0228",
      "start": 623.22,
      "end": 624.12,
      "text": "that was not real.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0229",
      "start": 625.02,
      "end": 627.06,
      "text": "Each time, the law's job was the same:",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0230",
      "start": 627.46,
      "end": 628.52,
      "text": "to find the line.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0231",
      "start": 629.1,
      "end": 631.04,
      "text": "The line between a stop and an arrest.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0232",
      "start": 631.76,
      "end": 634.54,
      "text": "Between identifying you and investigating you.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0233",
      "start": 634.74,
      "end": 636.98,
      "text": "Between a bold promise and a deliberate lie.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0023"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0234",
      "start": 644.04,
      "end": 646.24,
      "text": "That is what all of these cases really",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0235",
      "start": 646.24,
      "end": 649.3,
      "text": "are — not dramatic stories about famous people,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0236",
      "start": 649.74,
      "end": 651.9,
      "text": "but arguments about where a line falls,",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0237",
      "start": 651.9,
      "end": 655.8,
      "text": "as technology, money, and power keep moving it.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0238",
      "start": 656.36,
      "end": 659.24,
      "text": "The Constitution does not draw those lines once",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
      "id": "CAP-0239",
      "start": 659.24,
      "end": 659.82,
      "text": "and for all.",
      "chunk_id": "VC-0024"
    },
    {
